parameters.name: $SQ_PMS_Fact_Loss$
parameters.label: SQ_PMS_Fact_Loss
parameters.customQuery:
SELECT PMS_Fact_Loss.Policy_Key_Code, 
PMS_Fact_Loss.Policy_Key, 
PMS_Fact_Loss.Claim_Key, 
PMS_Fact_Loss.Major_Peril_ID, 
PMS_Fact_Loss.Risk_State_ID, 
PMS_Fact_Loss.Loss_Cause, 
PMS_Fact_Loss.Loss_Cause_Desc, 
PMS_Fact_Loss.StateLine, 
PMS_Fact_Loss.Account_Entered_Dt, 
PMS_Fact_Loss.Accident_Dt, 
PMS_Fact_Loss.Reported_Dt, 
PMS_Fact_Loss.Claim_Type, 
PMS_Fact_Loss.Loss_Adjustor_No, 
PMS_Fact_Loss.Loss_Paid_Amt, 
PMS_Fact_Loss.Loss_Paid_Recovery_Amt, 
PMS_Fact_Loss.Loss_Salvage, 
PMS_Fact_Loss.Loss_Subrogation_Amt, 
PMS_Fact_Loss.Loss_Ulae_Expense, 
PMS_Fact_Loss.Loss_Alae_Expense, 
PMS_Fact_Loss.Loss_Reserve_Amt, 
PMS_Fact_Loss.Loss_Reserve_For_Incurred_Loss, 
PMS_Fact_Loss.Transaction_CD, 
PMS_Fact_Loss.Transaction_Dt,
PMS_Fact_Loss.annual_statement_line
FROM
 dbo.PMS_Fact_Loss 
where Account_Entered_Dt >=dateadd(month, -1, cast(getdate() as date))

ORDER BY
PMS_Fact_Loss.Policy_Key_Code, 
PMS_Fact_Loss.Policy_Key, 
PMS_Fact_Loss.Claim_Key, 
PMS_Fact_Loss.Major_Peril_ID, 
PMS_Fact_Loss.Risk_State_ID, 
PMS_Fact_Loss.Loss_Cause, 
PMS_Fact_Loss.Loss_Cause_Desc, 
PMS_Fact_Loss.StateLine, 
PMS_Fact_Loss.Account_Entered_Dt, 
PMS_Fact_Loss.Accident_Dt, 
PMS_Fact_Loss.Reported_Dt, 
PMS_Fact_Loss.Claim_Type, 
PMS_Fact_Loss.Loss_Adjustor_No,
PMS_Fact_Loss.Transaction_CD, 
PMS_Fact_Loss.Transaction_Dt
